This paper is likely to belong to the category of Computer Science and Cryptography (cs.CR) as it deals with privacy and tracking behavior. It could also belong to the categories of Cybersecurity (cs.CY), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Multimedia (cs.MM), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) as these categories are related to the study of online tracking and advertising activity.
